last_episode_to_air.name: Graceful Giants: Pint-Sized
last_episode_to_air.overview: In the lush suburbs, Chip, a Golden Retriever pup tries to get in the middle of the action while a Great Dane born to an agility star mom finds her long legs aren't so conducive to being agile.

name: Too Cute
overview: Witness the miracle of cute, from a kitten's first tentative steps, to a puppy's first call to the wild. The first few months of their lives are an adorable adventure. These furry friends are simply too loveable, too curious, too cute!

episodes.name: Too Cute! Kittens
episodes.overview: Kitten owners go to great measures to take care of their fiercely independent pets as the birth and first few months of three separate kitten litters are documented in order to record all of the important moments in the kittens' lives.

episodes.name: Too Cute! Puppies
episodes.overview: The birth and first months of three different litters of puppies are followed; fawning owners do everything they can to accommodate their new pets; adorable moments of puppies' lives are shown as they eat, sleep and play.

episodes.name: Puppies and Ducklings
episodes.overview: Three delightful litters of puppies come of age; the first few months of Pugs', Mini-Australian Shepherds' and Rottweilers' lives are full of adventure, including an introduction to an agility course and lessons in duck-herding.

episodes.name: Kittens and Pocket Pets
episodes.overview: Featured are the epic adventures that take place during the first few months in the lives of Savannah, Siberian and Shorthaired kittens; cats grow up in a house full of guinea pigs, turtles and mice and run off to discover surprising, new territory.

episodes.name: Kitten Dolls
episodes.overview: The epic stories of three litters of kittens are followed as they grow from helpless "furballs" into rambunctious, young cats; hairless Sphynxes redine "cute"; Burmese cats explore new heights; tiny Ragdolls befriend German Shepherds.

episodes.name: Kitten Cottonballs
episodes.overview: Three litters of kittens pounce throughout the first few months of their lives; beautiful American Curl kittens get ready for life on the catwalk; a set of Tonkinese run circles around their mother; a Maine Coon shows his siblings who is boss.

episodes.name: Super Fluffy Puppies
episodes.overview: Three litters of puppies go from cute to cuter during the first few months of their lives; a trio of Rhodesian Ridgebacks runs circles around their mom; fluffy Chow Chow puppies have heaps of attitude; a Havanese has her paws full with five puppies.

episodes.name: Pool Puppies
episodes.overview: The coming-of-age stories of three litters are featured: three sweet puppies keep their Jack Russell Terrier mother active; a Portuguese Water Dog finds out that her litter may not be too fond of water; a Bullmastiff mother's four puppies keep growing.

episodes.name: Fluffy Puppies & Baby Goats
episodes.overview: Six fluffy Coton de Tulear puppies explore their farm home as one of them, Snowflake, struggles to find its place in the world until it meets Pipsqueak, an awkward baby pygmy goat; a mischievous German shepherd puppy struggles in obedience class.

episodes.name: Jungle Kitties & Baby Skunks
episodes.overview: Oreo, a tiny tuxedo kitten meets a similarly attired companion: Nellie the Skunk. Sputnik leads his Russian Blue siblings on a grand adventure. And, Ocicat Freckles tries to keep control of her five mini jungle cats.

episodes.name: Fuzzy Polar Puppies
episodes.overview: Nanook, a shy Chinook, is the only boy in a litter of four, training to be a sled dog. Rocky, the Labradoodle, and his brother Stanley grow up poolside. And Rollo and Pickles are wiener dogs who aspire to be athletes like their mom, a champion hotdog.

episodes.name: Spotted, Pampered Pups
episodes.overview: A shy Cavalier King Charles Spaniel is coaxed out of her shell by her peppy aunt. Then, everyone wants to be top dog in the Alaskan Malamute home. Finally, three Dalmatians grow into their spots as they show off their skills at the local fire station.

episodes.name: Sweetest Animal Friends
episodes.overview: In this "Best of" episode, viewers get a glimpse of the most adorable inter-species animal friendships. From roly-poly Ragdoll kittens and their German Shepherd playmate, to mini-Australian Shepherds and their quacking duckling pals, it's an extravaganza of cute.

episodes.name: Fluffy Puppy Party
episodes.overview: Pit bull puppy Thor discovers an urban paradise where it can be free; Collie pup Little Magic must learn to keep up with its pack mates; Chinese Crested puppies Bella and Buttons, though opposite in appearance, team up against a strange new creature.

episodes.name: Cuddly Kittens
episodes.overview: Toyger kitten Tonya overcomes her shy nature to befriend a large housemate. British Shorthair kittens audition for the role of "greeter" at a vet's office. And fluffy Ragamuffin Otto keep household chores at bay.

episodes.name: Puppy Love
episodes.overview: Raisin, a wrinkled Shar Pei, guards his toys from siblings Peaches and Pancake. Scout, a brave young Cairn Terrier, attempts an adventure all on his own. And Peanut, the smallest of a litter of Boxers, is steered to glory by his grandfather.

episodes.name: Extra Special Pets
episodes.overview: Five little piggies must befriend Penny the Spaniel and learn their new farm home; Clover, a mini-lop rabbit must assert herself with feisty brother Harley; Samson and Delilah teach their hoglet Pip and her spiky siblings about the great outdoors.

episodes.name: Curious Kittens
episodes.overview: Calico kittens mingle with canine clientele at a dog-grooming salon where their mother works. Exotic Shorthair kittens are born into the lap of luxury, but soon reveal their mischievous side. And a pair of Tabby kittens explore the great outdoors.

episodes.name: Kitten Beauties
episodes.overview: Godiva Kiss, a Birman beauty queen, is raising three kittens who may follow in her royal footsteps. Tofu, a Cornish Rex kitten, and his siblings befriend Donna the Iguana. Cutie, a tortoiseshell cat is raising twin brothers that are nothing alike.

episodes.name: Mighty Munchkins
episodes.overview: An adorable showdown takes place between Pucci the Chihuahua and the new Royal Himalayan kittens. Singapura mom Jasmine has a hard time keeping up with her tiny, energetic brood. Short-legged and long legged munchkin siblings navigate the world.

episodes.name: Tiny Giants
episodes.overview: Puck, a keeshond pup, befriends a flock of ducks on the farm while sister Tulip explores the woodshop. A little Great Dane named Marvin is adjusting to his fast-growing body. Cocker Spaniel pups look the same but certainly don't act the same.

episodes.name: Fluff and Feathers
episodes.overview: Lab mix rescue pup Sally is never seen far behind brother Safari, Pomeranian triplets Sparrow, Wren and Finch carry on mom Star and dad Tucker's job of watching over a feathered menagerie and Ibizan Hound puppies Carmen, Figaro and Arabella try to out chase each other.

episodes.name: Puppy Power
episodes.overview: Anya the Doberman pinscher and her human best friend, toddler Kaylee, have a big job keeping up with Anya's 12 new puppies. Runt beagle pup Roo hopes his nose will help him hunt with his sisters. Show dog Bichon Frise Angel breeds her champion brood.

episodes.name: Fluffiest Kittens
episodes.overview: In this best-of episode: Bold little Maine coon kitten Lulu tries to help her dad get along with her siblings. Persian kittens prepare to be like their show cat mom, Truly Elegant. Siberian twins Mittens and Socks are rescued from the closet by Maksim, the cat of the house.

episodes.name: Puppies and a Piggy
episodes.overview: One dozen goldendoodles take over a home and a pet pig's bed; a Westie chases after her wandering twin brother; Swiss mountain puppies find their stride.

episodes.name: Tiny Puppies, Big Paws
episodes.overview: A foursome of Neo-Mastiffs have big paws to fill if they're going to be be guard dogs like their Mom. A shy Chihuahua puppy learns that her tiny family have big hearts. And a litter of seven English Setters compete for first place.

episodes.name: Mischievous Puppies
episodes.overview: Irish terriers meet their bothersome teenage brother.  8 Corgis help on the farm, and an Akita puppy finds her place among her brothers.

episodes.name: Puffy Beach Kitties
episodes.overview: Spotted Bengal kittens are bowled over by a lumbering Newfoundland. 4 fluffy Norwegian Forest Cats dip their toes in the surf at their neighborhood beach, and, at a rescue home, 2 kittens find their way into the den mother's heart.

episodes.name: Puppies Growing Up
episodes.overview: Catch up 1 year later with German Shepherd, French Bulldog and Mini Australian Shepherd puppies.

episodes.name: Perfectly Precious Puppies
episodes.overview: Poodles, Basset Hounds and Bull Terrier puppies are featured.

episodes.name: Puppies Growing Up Fluffy
episodes.overview: Catching up with litters of Portuguese water dog, Rhodesian ridge-back and dachshund puppies after one year.

episodes.name: Rainbow Colored Kittens
episodes.overview: In a litter of six Maine Coon kitties, only boy Maurice struggles to fit in with his sisters. A quiet kitten with a limp tries to find his voice in a litter of super-chatty Siamese cats. And a shy black kitten tries to befriend an older butterscotch tabby

episodes.name: Kittens Growing Up
episodes.overview: Catching up with litters of Persian, Bengal and British shorthair kittens after one year.

episodes.name: Roly-Poly Puppies
episodes.overview: A shy Papillon puppy named Kitty comes out of her shell with the help of her siblings. A trio of St Bernard puppies follow their noses to big adventures. And finally, an Airedale Terrier named Merlin tries to disappear from her eight brothers and sisters.

episodes.name: Little Wildcats
episodes.overview: A black-and-white kitten plays with its adopted brother, a baby skunk; an orange tabby kitten tries to befriend a canine housemate; a Savannah kitten seeks a playmate.

episodes.name: Big Jobs, Little Paws
episodes.overview: Four tiny Tibetan Spaniels - all boys - are born into a family of watchdogs. A extra large litter of Newfoundland puppies take to the water as they train to be rescue dogs. And a patchwork puppy tries to blend into a family of Retriever Mixes.

episodes.name: Animal BFFs - Cuddly Bear, Cautious Kangaroo
episodes.overview:
A bear cub befriends a lonely German Shepherd. A deer and a kangaroo have their world turned upside down by a mischievous lemur. And a pygmy goat has a hard time fitting in until he meets a shy puppy.

Note: 30 min episode/special

episodes.name: Animal BFFs - Baby Baboon, Teacup Pig
episodes.overview:
A baby Baboon is taken under the wing of a Golden Retriever. A Teacup Pig and a Flemish Rabbit sneak away from their day jobs and get into trouble. And an adventurous goat and a timid lamb break out of their everyday routine.

Note: 30 min episode/special

episodes.name: Fuzzy Puppy Stars
episodes.overview: Star-struck Snow is a Great Pyrenees puppy who dreams of following in her movie star mom's paw prints. A pair of Border Collie pups will need to be brave if they're going to be champion herders. And a Scottish Terrier tries to win over the resident cat.

episodes.name: Mighty Mountain Puppies
episodes.overview: Two Bernese Mountain Dog pups bond with their barnyard neighbors. A trio of Shiba Inu girls challenge their spick and span mom with their messy ways. And, in a litter of mixed breed Chatham Hill Retrievers, a young pup takes after his boisterous dad.

episodes.name: Chilled Out Pups
episodes.overview: A dog spa hostess has her work cut out for her by 10 whippet pups; a mix-breed pup looks to fit in with sisters; mother's serene life is disrupted by a litter of 13 black Russian terriers.

episodes.name: Pint-Sized Pups and a Ferret
episodes.overview: A pup befriends a ferret.

episodes.name: Kittens in Wonderland
episodes.overview: Tabby litter befriends a bearded dragon; Alice the Burmese leads her brothers on an adventure; runt of Siberian litter plays with miniature horse named Kitty.

episodes.name: Fluffy Pups and Tater Tots
episodes.overview: A Chesapeake Bay Retriever is convinced he's the alpha dog, but his big cousin isn't about to roll over. Miniature Poodle Tater Tot is determined to prove she's the equal of her bigger, louder brothers. And a snowy, fussy Samoyed befriends a Dalmatian.

episodes.name: Tiny Watchdogs
episodes.overview: Litter of Yorkshire Terriers mess around with Guinea hens; Pippa deals with four new siblings; German Shepherd and Labrador Retriever train to be seeing-eye dogs.

episodes.name: Musical Kittens
episodes.overview: Turkish Van needs help from a dog to keep her kittens in check; six European Burmese have loud voices in musical home; pair of Persians raise trio.

episodes.name: Supersized Pups
episodes.overview: A Rat Terrier pup troes to find his place on a ranch full of rambunctious siblings. A stylish Briard named Fresco has to learn to take care of her 10 supersized pups. And finally, a Japanese Chin named Carly tries to spin her way into the spotlight.

episodes.name: Little Lion Pups
episodes.overview: A Bullmastiff puppy sticks to his aunt's side as he tries to follow in her footsteps and become a guard dog. A pair of Lowchen pups seek out additional family members. And, an Old English Sheepdog finds himself being herded by tiny sister.

episodes.name: Kittens and Canines
episodes.overview: A litter of orphaned kittens trail a pair of Dandy Dinmont Terriers. The only girl in a litter of four American Bobtails hunts for her place in the pack. And finally, a naughty Tonkinese kitten proves a handful for her prim and proper mom.

episodes.name: Tubby Puppies
episodes.overview: Dexter, a Bulldog who has aspirations to rise above his lazy siblings attempts to prove himself on the agility course. Then, a pack of pups who were rescued from the city streets find themselves in a barnyard full of strange beasts.

episodes.name: Chatty Kittens
episodes.overview: A Siamese named Chester tries to find some peace and quiet away from his eight noisy siblings; a British shorthair a cat clinic looks after her six kittens.

episodes.name: Kitten Puffs
episodes.overview: In a cozy cabin, a pair of Siberian soul mates’ relationship is put to the test with the birth of their fireball son Calvin. While at a cats only grooming salon, a Turkish Angora kitten named Izzie has to balance her personal style with life in the salon.

episodes.name: Muddy Puppies
episodes.overview: At a small farmhouse an adventurous Cairn Terrier named Doogie attempts to befriend a finicky house cat. While a pristine pack of Samoyed pups have to decide whose rules they’d rather follow – their tidy mom or their messy dad.

episodes.name: Puppies and Prickles
episodes.overview: In the countryside, a German Shepherd mom is training her troop of seven pups to be Search and Rescue dogs. While in the big city an African Pygmy Hedgehog named Prickle is looking for a soft and cuddly companion in a house full of Havanese puppies.

episodes.name: Puppy Giants
episodes.overview: An English Mastiff puppy named Dot searches for a little independence from her tag-a-long sister Olive. And Niles, a Small Munsterlander, tries to live up to his breed’s reputation as top notch hunting dogs, despite the distraction of his fun-loving mom.

episodes.name: Sock Puppies
episodes.overview: In a pack of nine Spinone Italianos, there’s only one thing that keeps a timid pup named Wally calm, his security sock. While a few miles away, a mischievous Pug named Oskar is a constant handful for his orderly librarian mom.

episodes.name: Puppy Posse
episodes.overview: A Siberian Husky has declared himself the leader of a pack of seven pups, but he'll need to back up his bravado with some real sledding smarts. And in a litter of a dozen Irish Red and White Setters, a little runt named Lil has to prove she can keep up.

episodes.name: Cuddly Kittens
episodes.overview: A pair of Shetland Sheepdogs are concerned that their only pup is getting distracted by the farm’s resident Pomeranian Gino. Plus, in a litter full of tailless Manx, one kitten named Charlie is born with a tail and needs to figure out he fits in.

episodes.name: Puppy Surprise
episodes.overview: At an urban animal shelter, a Maltese mix named Coco has a surprise litter, led by bold, only-boy Ralphie - while in the country, a restless Ragdoll kitten named Jolene might be more than her laid-back mom can handle.

episodes.name: Puppy Pros
episodes.overview: In a small town, a dog about town named Izzy brings a rare litter of Portuguese Podengo Pequeno pups into the world, led by go-getter Gisele. Meanwhile, an octuplet of Cockapoos train to be therapy dogs.

episodes.name: Fab & Furless Kittens
episodes.overview: The first months of adorable sets of elf cats and Abyssinian kittens are chronicled from their first steps to days of playful contact with new creatures.

episodes.name: Shy Kitties
episodes.overview: In a cozy home of Himalayans, a shy kitten named Hugo follows in his father's footsteps. While a rags to riches rescue mix brings her brood of puppies to their new dream home and only girl, Honey, makes an unlikely friend.

episodes.name: Rescue Kittens & Water Babies: Pint-Sized
episodes.overview: A pair of rescue kittens are welcomed into their foster home by a cat-loving rescue dog named Sweet Potato. While a Rhodesian Ridgeback pup named Rosie discovers, with the help of a lively older cousin, that swimming can be a whole lot of fun.

episodes.name: Super Pups: Pint-Sized
episodes.overview: Twin Dachshund pups, Lulu and Betty, discover their different personalities with a little bit of guidance from their free spirit father. While a show pup in training, Chinese Crested Dotty, forms an unlikely friendship with rescue Pitbull Bryan.

episodes.name: Graceful Giants: Pint-Sized
episodes.overview: In the lush suburbs, Chip, a Golden Retriever pup tries to get in the middle of the action while a Great Dane born to an agility star mom finds her long legs aren't so conducive to being agile.
